variant_descriptions.KUNPCKBW: Unpack 8-bit masks in k2 and k3 and write word result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KUNPCKWD: Unpack 16-bit masks in k2 and k3 and write doubleword result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KUNPCKDQ: Unpack 32-bit masks in k2 and k3 and write quadword result in k1.

op.text: Unpacks the lower 8/16/32 bits of the second and third operands (source operands) into the low part of the first operand (destination operand), starting from the low bytes. The result is zero-extended in the destination.
